{"tid":1988874,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中方據報向歐盟施壓 淡化批評中國散佈疫情虛假信息","createTime":"2020-04-25T13:19:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T13:26:41.000Z","uid":125193,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6cfe16f1d48b1578bc6ff14987138b51097a2782","tid":1988874,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T13:19:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522743-20200425.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522743-20200425.htm&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKjDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=a06f8582\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522743-20200425.htm&h=4f365011\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522743-20200425.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n外電報道，中國向歐盟施壓，阻止一份批評中國散佈新型冠狀病毒疫情虛假信息的報告發表，又迫使歐盟修改部分內容。<br />\n<br />\n《路透社》說，報告批評中國的部分內容被刪除和調整。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐歐盟使團和歐盟發言人也拒絕評論。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述四名外交人士透露，這份原定4月1日發表的報告，因為中方施壓而推遲發表，而報告對外與內部版本幾個地方作出改動，例如內部報告首頁上說，中國繼續在全球範圍散佈虛假信息，以轉移世人追究的視線，改善自己的國際形象，但對外版本則被刪除。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐歐盟使團團長張明星期五接受訪問時表示，虛假信息是共同的敵人，必須共同加以應對。"},{"pid":"1a3a3e43d119291176d7b199ef40135c7dd337ba","tid":1988874,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T13:21:12.000Z","msg":"中國巿場仲係咁有影響力？"},{"pid":"d88168b023da93879332b6c4bdc381967e594b5e","tid":1988874,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T13:24:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b83563d65bc2879e701e9a28253c809028a9da7","tid":1988874,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T13:26:41.000Z","msg":"歐洲人憎美國憎到寧願同普京維尼合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}